  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个医疗数据同步的流程图。核心场景是EMR系统（电子病历）和HIPAA合规的数据 Vault 之间的双向同步，还要对接实验室分析设备。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那EMR_Sync是起点吗？我理解为它先发起同步请求到HIPAA_Vault？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，EMR_Sync作为起点，先把数据推送到HIPAA_Vault做合规存储。然后Vault那边处理完会回调到EMR_Sync，形成一个闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把A（EMR_Sync）指向B（HIPAA_Vault），然后B再指回C（另一个EMR_Sync节点，代表回调）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来需要分支判断：回调回来的数据要送到LabAnalyzer做实验室分析。这里用菱形判断框，Analyzer会决定样本是否需要进一步诊断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "D",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "C指向D（LabAnalyzer菱形），然后D分出两条路：Yes走诊断引擎，No直接回到同步节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "F"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Yes分支到DiagnosticEngine，No分支回到EMR_Sync做常规归档。不过这里有个细节——两个分支最终要汇合到一个新的判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "F",
        "G"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "汇合到G？G也是一个菱形判断？它的判断逻辑是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "G"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "G是EMR_Sync的二次判断，检查当前数据状态是否需要重新同步到Vault。Yes就回到B（HIPAA_Vault），No则回到H（LabAnalyzer）做复测。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "G",
        "B",
        "H"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了：E和F都指向G，G的Yes回B，No去H。不过我发现H也是LabAnalyzer，和D重复了，需要区分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "F",
        "G",
        "H",
        "B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，H应该是另一个LabAnalyzer实例，代表复测流程，但名字确实容易混淆。不过Mermaid里可以先这样命名，实际部署是不同的微服务实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "H"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "了解，保留H作为复测节点。现在检查整体闭环：A→B→C→D→(Yes→E→G, No→F→G)→G→(Yes→B, No→H)。B被G指回来形成循环，符合设计吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "F",
        "G",
        "H"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。这个循环就是核心设计——诊断后的数据如果状态变更，需要重新进入HIPAA_Vault合规审查。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "G"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我注意到C和F都是EMR_Sync，A也是。三个EMR_Sync节点分别代表什么阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "C",
        "F"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "A是初始推送，C是Vault回调后的接收，F是无需诊断时的直接归档。虽然都是EMR_Sync服务，但处于流程的不同阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "C",
        "F"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整标签区分。最后确认：D和H都是LabAnalyzer，D是初检，H是复测，G的No分支到H形成复测回路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "H",
        "G"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这样整个sticengine就完整了。从EMR出发，经过Vault合规、Lab分析、诊断引擎，最终根据状态要么回Vault，要么复测。wchart结构清晰。",
